Source: sloc
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: @MAINTAINER@
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), zig (>= 0.15.2)
Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Homepage: https://github.com/@REPO@
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: sloc
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: fast source-lines-of-code counter with separate test totals
 A fast, standalone source-lines-of-code counter that separates code and test
 lines while skipping blanks, bracket-only lines, and single-line comments.
